    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302560/extras/e04258592ab7813dbf281ff230d40cf3.avif?t=1678409556\" width=600 height=132 /></span><br>颤栗》是一款合作式恐怖游戏，最多可以有4个人玩，至少要有1个人。你的目标是与你的团队或单独使用你的装备在被诅咒的地方探测邪恶的精神类型。<br><br><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302560/extras/57acbbaf692f8ed17a8d0cc17c56a8f0.webp?t=1678409556\" width=174 height=32 /></span><br>你将玩到的合作恐怖类型中最好的图形。使用虚幻引擎5开发。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302560/extras/c41914cd04f32eaa95c49352a15ab5d5.poster.avif?t=1678409556\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302560/extras/c41914cd04f32eaa95c49352a15ab5d5.webm?t=1678409556\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302560/extras/c41914cd04f32eaa95c49352a15ab5d5.mp4?t=1678409556\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302560/extras/8865c783cc3b2461fd40923050aff09a.webp?t=1678409556\" width=167 height=31 /></span><br>你在每场比赛中都会遇到随机事件和鬼魂</strong> 。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302560/extras/5a96a48e09ab6c4f48afd57c6971d0cd.poster.avif?t=1678409556\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302560/extras/5a96a48e09ab6c4f48afd57c6971d0cd.webm?t=1678409556\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302560/extras/5a96a48e09ab6c4f48afd57c6971d0cd.mp4?t=1678409556\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302560/extras/c0f254b542557490f979770919d06418.webp?t=1678409556\" width=168 height=32 /></span><br>除了与鬼魂交谈外，要小心你所说的话，被诅咒的地方会有相应的反应（你说的一个字就可以打开一扇秘密的门）</strong> 。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302560/extras/20e3ac32d1a3e2af7f54b99d73888cce.poster.avif?t=1678409556\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302560/extras/20e3ac32d1a3e2af7f54b99d73888cce.webm?t=1678409556\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302560/extras/20e3ac32d1a3e2af7f54b99d73888cce.mp4?t=1678409556\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302560/extras/fb1cdb1b23e10f5e6d1fa1c36ba7cea9.webp?t=1678409556\" width=115 height=32 /></span><br>你将能够邀请其他人到你的安全屋，你将能够选择超自然的地方来玩。你将有一个展示台，在那里你可以展示你的成就。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302560/extras/41c0023e3ae0c00d8669239ef63d1154.poster.avif?t=1678409556\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302560/extras/41c0023e3ae0c00d8669239ef63d1154.webm?t=1678409556\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302560/extras/41c0023e3ae0c00d8669239ef63d1154.mp4?t=1678409556\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302560/extras/91f6e4112ff560585ef1c79ade345d96.webp?t=1678409556\" width=123 height=30 /></span><br>用你赚来的钱，你可以改善你的安全屋或购买一个新的安全屋。你可以买一只宠物，让它和你一起站在安全屋里</strong> 。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302560/extras/125be8f58c9686fefee0694abc722036.poster.avif?t=1678409556\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302560/extras/125be8f58c9686fefee0694abc722036.webm?t=1678409556\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302560/extras/125be8f58c9686fefee0694abc722036.mp4?t=1678409556\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302560/extras/f8b70909b6f218c764b49bd99569c430.webp?t=1678409556\" width=120 height=32 /></span><br>多种地图和设备可供玩耍。每日和每周的任务。特殊日期的独特事件和任务。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302560/extras/8c7a61ab70736e24ba52a41622396220.poster.avif?t=1678409556\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302560/extras/8c7a61ab70736e24ba52a41622396220.webm?t=1678409556\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302560/extras/8c7a61ab70736e24ba52a41622396220.mp4?t=1678409556\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></strong>",
